title: [1508521049] Crispy Roast Duck Pancakes with Black Bean Dipping Sauce | Gordon Ramsay
description:
Everyone loves crispy duck pancakes - the Ramsay twist involves black bean dipping sauce as opposed to the traditional hoisin. Daughter Megan stops by to help with one of her favourite recipes.
